" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Straight leg raise maneuver",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 360px; height: 284px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The straight leg raise maneuver is used to determine the presence of radiculopathy. The maneuver can be performed in the sitting or lying position. The leg is gradually moved to the fully extended position. Ankle dorsiflexion can be added in full extension to bring out subtle cases. A positive maneuver reproduces the patient's pain; the test is inconclusive if tightness or pain is felt only in the hamstring area.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
